org.spf4j.ds

Class UpdateablePriorityQueue<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.spf4j.ds.UpdateablePriorityQueue<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - - the type of the elements in the queue.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Iterable<E>

    public final class UpdateablePriorityQueue<E>
extends Object
implements Iterable<E>, Serializable
    A priority queue which allows efficient element update. Element update can be either a replacement or element mutation. Implementation is based on jdk priority queue.
    Author:
    zoly
